Home Theater - September 2013


Home Theater this high-end consumer magazine celebrates the experience and technology of home theaters. Every issue features unique system-oriented product reviews, comparative product 'face-offs', comprehensive buyer's guides, dealer/product locator listings and all the information necessary to create a new 'home theater' system, or get the most out of an existing system.




                      English | PDF | 84 Pages | 102.40 Mb
